                <p class="hero-description">Our standard cleaning service is the perfect solution for maintaining a clean, healthy home without the stress. Designed for regular visits, this comprehensive service keeps your Ocala home looking its best week after week.</p>
                <div class="hero-buttons">
                    <a href="/book-now" class="btn btn-primary">Book Now</a>
                    <a href="tel:+13527644747" class="btn btn-secondary">Call (352) 764-4747</a>
