            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services" id="services">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">What is Standard Cleaning in Ocala?</h2>
            <p style="text-align: center; color: #666; margin-bottom: 3rem; font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
                Standard cleaning is our regular maintenance service designed to keep your home consistently clean and healthy. Perfect for busy Ocala families who want to come home to a fresh, spotless space without lifting a finger.
            </p>
            
            <div class="services-grid">
                <div class="service-card featured">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>What's Included in Standard Cleaning</h3>
                    <p>Our comprehensive standard cleaning service covers all the essential areas of your home to maintain cleanliness and hygiene.</p>
                    <ul class="service-list">
                        <li><strong>Kitchen:</strong> Countertop sanitization, appliance exterior cleaning, sink scrubbing, floor mopping</li>
                        <li><strong>Bathrooms:</strong> Toilet, tub, and shower cleaning, mirror polishing, floor sanitization</li>
                        <li><strong>Bedrooms:</strong> Dusting surfaces, vacuuming, bed making, trash removal</li>
                        <li><strong>Living Areas:</strong> Dusting furniture, vacuuming carpets, mopping floors</li>
                        <li><strong>Throughout Home:</strong> Emptying trash, dusting baseboards (reachable), wiping light switches</li>
                        <li>Window sill dusting</li>
                        <li>Cobweb removal</li>
                        <li>Door and cabinet front wiping</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Perfect Frequency for Ocala Homes</h3>
                    <p>Choose the schedule that works best for your lifestyle and budget:</p>
                    <ul class="service-list">
                        <li><strong>Weekly:</strong> Ideal for families with kids, pets, or allergies - maintains highest cleanliness</li>
                        <li><strong>Bi-weekly:</strong> Most popular choice - perfect balance for busy professionals</li>
                        <li><strong>Monthly:</strong> Great for smaller households or as a supplement to your own cleaning</li>
                        <li>Consistent scheduling means better rates</li>
                        <li>Same team assigned when possible</li>
                        <li>Easy to adjust frequency as needed</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-sparkles"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Standard vs. Deep Cleaning</h3>
                    <p>Understanding the difference helps you choose the right service:</p>
                    <ul class="service-list">
                        <li><strong>Standard:</strong> Regular maintenance, surface cleaning, routine tasks</li>
                        <li><strong>Deep:</strong> Detailed cleaning including inside appliances, baseboards, light fixtures</li>
                        <li>Start with deep cleaning, maintain with standard</li>
                        <li>Standard cleaning maintains cleanliness between deep cleans</li>
                        <li>Most Ocala homes need deep cleaning 2-4 times per year</li>
                        <li>Florida humidity makes regular cleaning essential</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Why Standard Cleaning is Essential in Ocala -->
            <div style="margin-top: 3rem; background: white; padding: 3rem; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
                <h3 style="color: #2f5047; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Why Standard Cleaning is Essential for Ocala Homes</h3>
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
                    <div>
                        <h4 style="color: #ff8057; margin-bottom: 1rem;"><i class="fas fa-tint" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>Florida Humidity</h4>
                        <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6;">Ocala's humid climate means dust, mold, and mildew can accumulate quickly. Regular standard cleaning prevents buildup and maintains a healthy indoor environment.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 style="color: #ff8057; margin-bottom: 1rem;"><i class="fas fa-leaf" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>Pollen & Allergens</h4>
                        <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6;">With year-round growing seasons, Ocala homes need consistent cleaning to manage pollen and allergens that affect indoor air quality.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 style="color: #ff8057; margin-bottom: 1rem;"><i class="fas fa-sun" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>Active Lifestyle</h4>
                        <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6;">From horse farms to outdoor activities, Ocala residents track in more dirt. Standard cleaning keeps your home fresh despite an active lifestyle.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Standard Cleaning Process -->
            <div style="margin-top: 3rem; background: #f8fafa; padding: 3rem; border-radius: 15px;">
                <h3 style="color: #2f5047; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Our Standard Cleaning Process</h3>
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;">
                    <div style="text-align: center;">
                        <div style="background: #ff8057; color: white; width: 60px; height: 60px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 1rem; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold;">1</div>
                        <h4 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Top to Bottom</h4>
                        <p style="color: #666;">We clean from ceiling to floor, ensuring dust and debris don't resettle on cleaned surfaces.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="text-align: center;">
                        <div style="background: #ff8057; color: white; width: 60px; height: 60px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 1rem; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold;">2</div>
