                        <p style="color: #666;">Systematic approach ensures nothing is missed and your home is thoroughly cleaned.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="text-align: center;">
                        <div style="background: #ff8057; color: white; width: 60px; height: 60px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 1rem; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold;">3</div>
                        <h4 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Quality Check</h4>
                        <p style="color: #666;">Final walkthrough to ensure every area meets our high standards before we leave.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="text-align: center;">
                        <div style="background: #ff8057; color: white; width: 60px; height: 60px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 1rem; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold;">4</div>
                        <h4 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Consistent Results</h4>
                        <p style="color: #666;">Same high-quality clean every visit, with notes kept about your preferences.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 3rem; text-align: center; background: #f8fafa; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 15px;">
                <h3 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Service Areas for Standard Cleaning</h3>
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem;">
                    <div>
                        <h4 style="color: #ff8057;">Stone Creek</h4>
                        <p>Luxury home cleaning for Stone Creek's beautiful community</p>
                        <a href="/stone-creek" class="btn btn-secondary" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 style="color: #ff8057;">Oak Run</h4>
                        <p>Professional cleaning for Oak Run's 55+ active adult community</p>
                        <a href="/oak-run" class="btn btn-secondary" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 style="color: #ff8057;">The Villages</h4>
                        <p>Trusted cleaning services throughout The Villages</p>
                        <a href="/the-villages" class="btn btn-secondary" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                    <div>
