                <div style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                        <h4 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 1rem;">What's the difference between standard and deep cleaning?</h4>
                        <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6;">Standard cleaning maintains your home's cleanliness with regular surface cleaning, dusting, vacuuming, and sanitizing. Deep cleaning includes detailed tasks like cleaning inside appliances, scrubbing baseboards, and cleaning light fixtures. We recommend starting with a deep clean, then maintaining with standard cleaning.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                        <h4 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 1rem;">How often should I schedule standard cleaning in Ocala?</h4>
                        <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6;">Most Ocala families choose bi-weekly standard cleaning as it provides the perfect balance of cleanliness and value. However, homes with pets, children, or allergy sufferers often benefit from weekly cleaning. Monthly cleaning works well for smaller households or empty nesters.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                        <h4 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Do I need to be home during standard cleaning?</h4>
                        <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6;">No, many of our regular clients provide us with a key or access code. We're fully licensed, insured, and all team members are background-checked. We'll lock up when we're done and can send you a text confirmation.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                        <h4 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 1rem;">What should I do before the cleaning team arrives?</h4>
                        <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6;">Simply pick up personal items, toys, and clutter from surfaces so our team can focus on cleaning rather than organizing. Secure any valuables and let us know about any special instructions or areas that need extra attention.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div>
                        <h4 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 1rem;">How long does standard cleaning take?</h4>
                        <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6;">Typically, standard cleaning takes 1.5-3 hours depending on your home's size and condition. First-time cleanings may take longer as we learn your home's layout. Regular clients often see faster service as our teams become familiar with your space.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact" id="contact">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Ready for Consistent, Reliable Cleaning?</h2>
            <div style="text-align: center; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                    Start enjoying a consistently clean home with our professional standard cleaning service. Get your free quote today and discover why Ocala families trust us for their regular cleaning needs.
                </p>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                    <a href="/book-now" class="btn btn-primary">Book Now</a>
                    <a href="tel:+13527644747" class="btn btn-secondary">Call (352) 764-4747</a>
